<!-- search -->
<record :id="search.id" model="ir.ui.view">
    <field name="name">{{search.name}}</field>
    <field name="model">{{model._modelName}}</field>
    <field name="arch" type="xml">
        <search :string="search.name">
            {{search.fields}}
            {{search.filters}}
            <group expand="1" string="分组">
                {{search.groups}}
            </group>
        </search>
    </field>
</record>
